From: David Woodhouse <dwmw@amazon.co.uk>

When the Xen guest asks to unplug *emulated* NICs, it's kind of unhelpful
also to unplug the peer of the *Xen* PV NIC.

Signed-off-by: David Woodhouse <dwmw@amazon.co.uk>
